<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>BookSphere — Premium Reading Platform</title>

    <!-- ============================================================
    STYLES (same as before, with minor additions for file upload)
    ============================================================ -->
    <style>
        /* ----- RESET & BASE ----- */
        *,
        *::before,
        *::after {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --primary: #007AFF;
            --primary-hover: #0055CC;
            --bg: #F5F5F7;
            --card: #FFFFFF;
            --text: #1C1C1E;
            --text-secondary: #6E6E73;
            --text-tertiary: #8E8E93;
            --border: #E5E5EA;
            --shadow-sm: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            --shadow-md: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            --shadow-lg: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
            --radius: 16px;
            --radius-sm: 10px;
            --radius-full: 9999px;
            --transition: 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
            --font: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Display",
                "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            --max-width: 1280px;
            --nav-height: 64px;
            --reader-font-size: 18px;
            --reader-line-height: 1.8;
            --reader-font-family: "Georgia", "Times New Roman", serif;
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            :root {
                --bg: #0A0A0C;
                --card: #1C1C1E;
                --text: #F5F5F7;
                --text-secondary: #AEAEB2;
                --text-tertiary: #8E8E93;
                --border: #2C2C2E;
                --shadow-sm: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
                --shadow-md: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
                --shadow-lg: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            }
        }

        html {
            font-size: 16px;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font);
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
            min-height: 100vh;
            transition: background var(--transition), color var(--transition);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: transparent;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: var(--text-tertiary);
            border-radius: var(--radius-full);
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: var(--max-width);
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 24px;
        }

        .sr-only {
            position: absolute;
            width: 1px;
            height: 1px;
            padding: 0;
            margin: -1px;
            overflow: hidden;
            clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
            border: 0;
        }

        .hidden {
            display: none !important;
        }

        .flex {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .flex-col {
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .gap-1 {
            gap: 4px;
        }
        .gap-2 {
            gap: 8px;
        }
        .gap-3 {
            gap: 12px;
        }
        .gap-4 {
            gap: 16px;
        }
        .gap-6 {
            gap: 24px;
        }
        .gap-8 {
            gap: 32px;
        }
        .justify-between {
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .justify-center {
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .items-center {
            align-items: center;
        }
        .flex-1 {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .text-secondary {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }
        .text-tertiary {
            color: var(--text-tertiary);
        }
        .text-sm {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }
        .text-xs {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
        }
        .font-medium {
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .font-semibold {
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .font-bold {
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .mt-2 {
            margin-top: 8px;
        }
        .mt-4 {
            margin-top: 16px;
        }
        .mt-6 {
            margin-top: 24px;
        }
        .mt-8 {
            margin-top: 32px;
        }
        .mb-2 {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .mb-4 {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .mb-6 {
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .mb-8 {
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 10px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: var(--radius-full);
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all var(--transition);
            text-decoration: none;
            background: var(--card);
            color: var(--text);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            min-height: 44px;
            min-width: 44px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }
        .btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.97);
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: #fff;
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: var(--primary-hover);
            border-color: var(--primary-hover);
        }
        .btn-ghost {
            background: transparent;
            border-color: transparent;
            box-shadow: none;
        }
        .btn-ghost:hover {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            box-shadow: none;
            transform: none;
        }
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .btn-ghost:hover {
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            }
        }
        .btn-sm {
            padding: 6px 16px;
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            min-height: 34px;
        }
        .btn-icon {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            padding: 0;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        /* ----- NAVIGATION ----- */
        .navbar {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            background: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.82);
            backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            height: var(--nav-height);
            transition: background var(--transition), border-color var(--transition);
        }
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .navbar {
                background: rgba(10, 10, 12, 0.85);
            }
        }
        .navbar .container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            height: 100%;
        }
        .nav-brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text);
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .nav-brand svg {
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .nav-actions {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4px;
        }
        .nav-actions .btn {
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            box-shadow: none;
            padding: 8px;
            min-width: 40px;
            min-height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }
        .nav-actions .btn:hover {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            transform: none;
        }
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .nav-actions .btn:hover {
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            }
        }
        .nav-actions .btn svg {
            display: block;
        }

        /* ----- CATEGORIES SCROLL ----- */
        .categories-scroll {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            padding: 16px 0 12px;
            scrollbar-width: none;
            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
            scroll-snap-type: x proximity;
        }
        .categories-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }
        .category-pill {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-full);
            background: var(--card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all var(--transition);
            scroll-snap-align: start;
            white-space: nowrap;
            user-select: none;
        }
        .category-pill:hover {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: #fff;
            border-color: var(--primary);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }
        .category-pill.active {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: #fff;
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* ----- SECTION HEADERS ----- */
        .section-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: baseline;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .section-header h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        .section-header .see-all {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 500;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            font-family: var(--font);
            transition: opacity var(--transition);
        }
        .section-header .see-all:hover {
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        /* ----- BOOK CARDS ----- */
        .books-horizontal {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            padding: 4px 0 16px;
            scrollbar-width: none;
            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
            scroll-snap-type: x proximity;
        }
        .books-horizontal::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }
        .book-card {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            width: 200px;
            background: var(--card);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            transition: all var(--transition);
            cursor: pointer;
            scroll-snap-align: start;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .book-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }
        .book-card:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
        }
        .book-card .cover {
            aspect-ratio: 2 / 3;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #e8e8ed, #d5d5dd);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .book-card .cover {
                background: linear-gradient(145deg, #2c2c2e, #1c1c1e);
            }
        }
        .book-card .cover .cover-emoji {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            opacity: 0.6;
        }
        .book-card .cover .progress-ring {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 10px;
            right: 10px;
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .book-card .cover .file-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            right: 10px;
            background: rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-full);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        }
        .book-card .info {
            padding: 14px 16px 16px;
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 4px;
        }
        .book-card .info .title {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            line-height: 1.3;
            display: -webkit-box;
            -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .book-card .info .author {
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }
        .book-card .info .meta {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-top: 6px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-tertiary);
        }
        .book-card .info .meta .dot {
            width: 3px;
            height: 3px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--text-tertiary);
        }
        .book-card .info .btn {
            margin-top: 10px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 8px;
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
        }

        /* Grid cards */
        .books-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(160px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
        }
        .books-grid .book-card {
            width: 100%;
        }
        .books-grid .book-card .cover {
            aspect-ratio: 2 / 3;
        }
        .books-grid .book-card .info .title {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        /* ----- BOOK DETAIL PAGE ----- */
        .book-detail {
            padding: 32px 0 48px;
        }
        .book-detail .hero {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
            gap: 40px;
            align-items: start;
        }
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .book-detail .hero {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 24px;
            }
        }
        .book-detail .hero .cover-large {
            aspect-ratio: 2 / 3;
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #e8e8ed, #d5d5dd);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 5rem;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 220px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
        }
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .book-detail .hero .cover-large {
                background: linear-gradient(145deg, #2c2c2e, #1c1c1e);
            }
        }
        .book-detail .hero .cover-large .file-badge-lg {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 12px;
            right: 12px;
            background: rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.9);
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-full);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        }
        .book-detail .hero .details h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .book-detail .hero .details .author {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .book-detail .hero .details .meta-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 16px 24px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .book-detail .hero .details .meta-list span {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }
        .book-detail .hero .details .description {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .book-detail .hero .details .actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        .book-detail .hero .details .actions .btn {
            min-width: 100px;
        }
        .book-detail .file-info {
            margin-top: 16px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            background: var(--card);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        .book-detail .file-info .file-details {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }
        .book-detail .file-info .file-details .file-icon {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        .book-detail .progress-section {
            margin-top: 32px;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            background: var(--card);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }
        .book-detail .progress-section .progress-label {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .book-detail .progress-section .progress-bar {
            height: 4px;
            background: var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-full);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .book-detail .progress-section .progress-bar .fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--primary);
            border-radius: var(--radius-full);
            transition: width 0.6s ease;
            width: 0%;
        }

        /* ----- READING MODE ----- */
        .reader-view {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            z-index: 200;
            background: var(--bg);
            display: none;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .reader-view.active {
            display: flex;
        }
        .reader-toolbar {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.92);
            backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            flex-shrink: 0;
            min-height: 56px;
        }
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .reader-toolbar {
                background: rgba(10, 10, 12, 0.92);
            }
        }
        .reader-toolbar .left,
        .reader-toolbar .right {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        .reader-toolbar .title {
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            max-width: 200px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
        }
        .reader-content {
            flex: 1;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding: 40px 24px 80px;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
        }
        .reader-content .chapter-title {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        .reader-content .chapter-body {
            font-size: var(--reader-font-size);
            line-height: var(--reader-line-height);
            font-family: var(--reader-font-family);
            max-width: 720px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .reader-content .chapter-body p {
            margin-bottom: 1.2em;
        }
        .reader-content .chapter-body h2 {
            font-size: 1.4em;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 1.6em 0 0.6em;
            font-family: var(--font);
        }
        .reader-content .chapter-body h3 {
            font-size: 1.15em;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 1.4em 0 0.4em;
            font-family: var(--font);
        }
        .reader-content .chapter-body blockquote {
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin: 1.2em 0;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .reader-content .chapter-body img {
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            margin: 1.2em 0;
        }
        .reader-content .chapter-body .footnote {
            font-size: 0.85em;
            color: var(--text-tertiary);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding-top: 0.8em;
            margin-top: 1.2em;
        }
        /* PDF viewer inside reader */
        .reader-content .pdf-viewer {
            width: 100%;
            height: calc(100vh - 140px);
            border: none;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            background: var(--bg);
        }
        .reader-content .file-content-text {
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            word-wrap: break-word;
            font-family: var(--reader-font-family);
            font-size: var(--reader-font-size);
            line-height: var(--reader-line-height);
            max-width: 720px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .reader-footer {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.92);
            backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(20px);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            min-height: 56px;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .reader-footer {
                background: rgba(10, 10, 12, 0.92);
            }
        }
        .reader-footer .progress-text {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-tertiary);
            min-width: 70px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .reader-footer .nav-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .reader-settings {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 72px;
            right: 24px;
            background: var(--card);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            padding: 20px 24px;
            min-width: 240px;
            display: none;
            z-index: 10;
        }
        .reader-settings.open {
            display: block;
        }
        .reader-settings label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .reader-settings select,
        .reader-settings input[type="range"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 6px 10px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .reader-settings .setting-group {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .reader-settings .setting-group:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        /* ----- CATEGORY PAGE ----- */
        .category-header {
            padding: 32px 0 24px;
        }
        .category-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        .category-header .count {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
        }

        /* ----- PROFILE ----- */
        .profile-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 24px;
            padding: 32px 0 24px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .profile-header .avatar {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #5856D6);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .profile-header .name {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .profile-header .email {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }
        .profile-stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(120px, 1fr));
            gap: 16px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        .profile-stats .stat {
            background: var(--card);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .profile-stats .stat .number {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .profile-stats .stat .label {
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }
        .profile-sections {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 24px;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .profile-sections {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
        .profile-sections .section-card {
            background: var(--card);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            padding: 20px 24px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .profile-sections .section-card h3 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .profile-sections .section-card .item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .profile-sections .section-card .item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .profile-sections .section-card .item .emoji {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        /* ----- SEARCH OVERLAY ----- */
        .search-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            z-index: 300;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            display: none;
            align-items: flex-start;
            justify-content: center;
            padding-top: 80px;
        }
        .search-overlay.open {
            display: flex;
        }
        .search-modal {
            background: var(--card);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            max-width: 640px;
            width: 90%;
            padding: 24px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            max-height: 80vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }
        .search-modal input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            border: 2px solid var(--border);
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            font-family: var(--font);
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            transition: border-color var(--transition);
            outline: none;
        }
        .search-modal input:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }
        .search-modal .results {
            margin-top: 16px;
        }
        .search-modal .results .result-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background var(--transition);
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            padding: 10px 12px;
        }
        .search-modal .results .result-item:hover {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
        }
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .search-modal .results .result-item:hover {
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            }
        }
        .search-modal .results .result-item .cover-sm {
            width: 40px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            background: var(--border);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .search-modal .results .result-item .info .title {
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .search-modal .results .result-item .info .sub {
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        /* ----- ADMIN PANEL ----- */
        .admin-panel {
            padding: 24px 0 48px;
        }
        .admin-panel .admin-nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .admin-panel .admin-nav .btn {
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            padding: 8px 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            box-shadow: none;
        }
        .admin-panel .admin-nav .btn:hover {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            transform: none;
        }
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .admin-panel .admin-nav .btn:hover {
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            }
        }
        .admin-panel .admin-nav .btn.active {
            color: var(--primary);
            background: rgba(0, 122, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .admin-panel .admin-section {
            display: none;
        }
        .admin-panel .admin-section.active {
            display: block;
        }
        .admin-panel .admin-card {
            background: var(--card);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            padding: 24px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .admin-panel .admin-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .admin-panel .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .admin-panel .form-group label {
            display: block;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }
        .admin-panel .form-group input,
        .admin-panel .form-group textarea,
        .admin-panel .form-group select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px 14px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            transition: border-color var(--transition);
            outline: none;
        }
        .admin-panel .form-group input:focus,
        .admin-panel .form-group textarea:focus,
        .admin-panel .form-group select:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }
        .admin-panel .form-group textarea {
            min-height: 120px;
            resize: vertical;
        }
        .admin-panel .form-group .file-upload-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border: 2px dashed var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            transition: border-color var(--transition);
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .admin-panel .form-group .file-upload-wrapper:hover {
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }
        .admin-panel .form-group .file-upload-wrapper .file-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            flex: 1;
        }
        .admin-panel .form-group .file-upload-wrapper .file-info .file-name {
            color: var(--text);
            font-weight: 500;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .admin-panel .form-group .file-upload-wrapper input[type="file"] {
            position: absolute;
            width: 0.1px;
            height: 0.1px;
            opacity: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        .admin-panel .form-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 16px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .admin-book-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .admin-book-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .admin-book-item .cover-sm {
            width: 40px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            background: var(--border);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .admin-book-item .info {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .admin-book-item .info .title {
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .admin-book-item .info .sub {
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }
        .admin-book-item .actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        /* ----- TOAST ----- */
        .toast {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 24px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(20px);
            background: var(--card);
            color: var(--text);
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-full);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            font-family: var(--font);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            z-index: 999;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
            max-width: 90%;
            text-align: center;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .toast.show {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
        }

        /* ----- RESPONSIVE ----- */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 0 16px;
            }
            .book-card {
                width: 160px;
            }
            .books-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(140px, 1fr));
                gap: 16px;
            }
            .book-detail .hero {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .book-detail .hero .cover-large {
                max-width: 180px;
            }
            .book-detail .hero .details h1 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
            .reader-content {
                padding: 24px 16px 80px;
            }
            .reader-toolbar .title {
                max-width: 120px;
            }
            .profile-header {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .search-modal {
                width: 95%;
                padding: 16px;
            }
            .admin-panel .admin-card {
                padding: 16px;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .book-card {
                width: 140px;
            }
            .books-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(120px, 1fr));
                gap: 12px;
            }
            .book-card .info {
                padding: 10px 12px 12px;
            }
            .book-card .info .title {
                font-size: 0.8125rem;
            }
            .section-header h2 {
                font-size: 1.25rem;
            }
            .reader-toolbar {
                padding: 8px 12px;
            }
            .reader-footer {
                padding: 8px 12px;
            }
            .reader-content .chapter-title {
                font-size: 1.25rem;
            }
        }

        /* ----- ANIMATIONS ----- */
        .fade-in {
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease forwards;
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(12px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        .slide-up {
            animation: slideUp 0.4s ease forwards;
        }
        @keyframes slideUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        .scale-in {
            animation: scaleIn 0.35s ease forwards;
        }
        @keyframes scaleIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.95);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }
        .page {
            display: none;
            animation: pageIn 0.4s ease forwards;
        }
        .page.active {
            display: block;
        }
        @keyframes pageIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(16px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .toggle-wrap {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .toggle {
            width: 48px;
            height: 28px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-full);
            background: var(--border);
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
            transition: background var(--transition);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .toggle.active {
            background: var(--primary);
        }
        .toggle .knob {
            width: 22px;
            height: 22px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #fff;
            position: absolute;
            top: 3px;
            left: 3px;
            transition: transform var(--transition);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }
        .toggle.active .knob {
            transform: translateX(20px);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- ============================================================
    NAVIGATION
    ============================================================ -->
    <nav class="navbar" role="navigation" aria-label="Main navigation">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="nav-brand" data-page="home" aria-label="BookSphere home">
                <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <rect x="4" y="4" width="20" height="20" rx="4" stroke="#007AFF" stroke-width="2.5" />
                    <path d="M10 8L18 8" stroke="#007AFF" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
                    <path d="M10 13L16 13" stroke="#007AFF" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
                    <path d="M10 18L14 18" stroke="#007AFF" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
                </svg>
                <span>BookSphere</span>
            </div>

            <div class="nav-actions">
                <button class="btn btn-ghost" id="searchToggle" aria-label="Search" title="Search">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
                        <circle cx="9" cy="9" r="6" />
                        <path d="M13.5 13.5L18 18" />
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <button class="btn btn-ghost" id="profileToggle" aria-label="Profile" title="Profile" data-page="profile">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
                        <circle cx="10" cy="7" r="3.5" />
                        <path d="M3 17C3 13.5 5.5 11 10 11C14.5 11 17 13.5 17 17" />
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <button class="btn btn-ghost" id="adminToggle" aria-label="Admin" title="Admin" data-page="admin">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
                        <rect x="3" y="8" width="14" height="10" rx="1.5" />
                        <path d="M7 8V5C7 3.5 8 2 10 2C12 2 13 3.5 13 5V8" />
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- ============================================================
    MAIN CONTENT
    ============================================================ -->
    <main>

        <!-- HOME PAGE -->
        <section class="page active" id="page-home" role="main" aria-label="Home">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="categories-scroll" id="categoriesContainer" role="tablist" aria-label="Book categories">
                </div>

                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2>Featured</h2>
                    <button class="see-all" data-page="category" data-category="all">See All</button>
                </div>
                <div class="books-horizontal" id="featuredBooks"></div>

                <div class="section-header" style="margin-top:32px;">
                    <h2>Recently Added</h2>
                    <button class="see-all" data-page="category" data-category="all">See All</button>
                </div>
                <div class="books-grid" id="recentlyAdded"></div>

                <div class="section-header" style="margin-top:32px;">
                    <h2>Recommended For You</h2>
                    <button class="see-all" data-page="category" data-category="all">See All</button>
                </div>
                <div class="books-grid" id="recommendedBooks"></div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- BOOK DETAIL -->
        <section class="page" id="page-book" role="main" aria-label="Book detail">
            <div class="container book-detail" id="bookDetail"></div>
        </section>

        <!-- CATEGORY -->
        <section class="page" id="page-category" role="main" aria-label="Category">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="category-header" id="categoryHeader">
                    <h1 id="categoryTitle">Category</h1>
                    <span class="count" id="categoryCount">0 books</span>
                </div>
                <div class="books-grid" id="categoryBooks"></div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- PROFILE -->
        <section class="page" id="page-profile" role="main" aria-label="Profile">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="profile-header">
                    <div class="avatar" id="profileAvatar">JD</div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="name" id="profileName">John Doe</div>
                        <div class="email" id="profileEmail">john@booksphere.com</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="profile-stats" id="profileStats"></div>
                <div class="profile-sections">
                    <div class="section-card">
                        <h3>📚 Recently Read</h3>
                        <div id="recentlyReadList"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section-card">
                        <h3>🔖 Bookmarks</h3>
                        <div id="bookmarksList"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section-card">
                        <h3>❤️ Favorites</h3>
                        <div id="favoritesList"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section-card">
                        <h3>⚙️ Settings</h3>
                        <div class="toggle-wrap">
                            <span>Dark Mode</span>
                            <div class="toggle" id="darkModeToggle" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="Toggle dark mode">
                                <div class="knob"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ADMIN -->
        <section class="page" id="page-admin" role="main" aria-label="Admin panel">
            <div class="container admin-panel">
                <h1 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;">Admin Panel</h1>
                <p class="text-secondary" style="margin-bottom:20px;">Manage your books, categories, and content.</p>

                <div class="admin-nav" role="tablist">
                    <button class="btn active" data-admin-tab="dashboard">Dashboard</button>
                    <button class="btn" data-admin-tab="books">Books</button>
                    <button class="btn" data-admin-tab="editor">Editor</button>
                    <button class="btn" data-admin-tab="categories">Categories</button>
                    <button class="btn" data-admin-tab="settings">Settings</button>
                </div>

                <!-- Dashboard -->
                <div class="admin-section active" id="admin-dashboard">
                    <div class="admin-card">
                        <h3>📊 Overview</h3>
                        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(140px,1fr));gap:16px;" id="adminStats"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="admin-card">
                        <h3>📖 Recent Books</h3>
                        <div id="adminRecentBooks"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Books List -->
                <div class="admin-section" id="admin-books">
                    <div class="admin-card">
                        <h3>All Books</h3>
                        <div id="adminBookList"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Editor -->
                <div class="admin-section" id="admin-editor">
                    <div class="admin-card">
                        <h3 id="editorTitle">✏️ Create New Book</h3>
                        <form id="bookEditorForm" autocomplete="off">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="bookTitle">Book Title</label>
                                <input type="text" id="bookTitle" placeholder="e.g. The Art of Islamic Pattern" required />
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="bookSubtitle">Subtitle</label>
                                <input type="text" id="bookSubtitle" placeholder="e.g. A Visual Journey" />
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="bookAuthor">Author</label>
                                <input type="text" id="bookAuthor" placeholder="e.g. Jane Smith" required />
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="bookCategory">Category</label>
                                <select id="bookCategory"></select>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="bookDescription">Description</label>
                                <textarea id="bookDescription" placeholder="A brief description of the book..." rows="4"></textarea>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="bookCoverEmoji">Cover Emoji</label>
                                <input type="text" id="bookCoverEmoji" placeholder="e.g. 📘" maxlength="2" style="width:80px;" />
                            </div>

                            <!-- === NEW: File Upload === -->
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label>Upload Book File (PDF, EPUB, TXT)</label>
                                <div class="file-upload-wrapper" id="fileUploadWrapper">
                                    <input type="file" id="bookFileInput" accept=".pdf,.epub,.txt,application/pdf,application/epub+zip,text/plain" />
                                    <div class="file-info" id="fileInfo">
                                        <span class="file-icon" id="fileIcon">📄</span>
                                        <span>
                                            <span class="file-name" id="fileDisplayName">No file selected</span>
                                            <span class="text-xs text-tertiary" id="fileSizeDisplay"></span>
                                        </span>
                                    </div>
                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-ghost" id="clearFileBtn" style="display:none;">✕</button>
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-tertiary" style="margin-top:4px;">Upload a PDF, EPUB, or TXT file. The file will be stored in your browser.</div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label>Chapters</label>
                                <div id="chapterList"></div>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-ghost" id="addChapterBtn" style="margin-top:8px;">+ Add Chapter</button>
                                <div class="text-xs text-tertiary" style="margin-top:4px;">Chapters are only used for books without an uploaded file.</div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="form-actions">
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="saveBookBtn">Save Book</button>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-ghost" id="deleteBookBtn" style="color:#FF3B30;display:none;">Delete</button>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-ghost" id="cancelEditBtn" style="display:none;">Cancel</button>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Categories -->
                <div class="admin-section" id="admin-categories">
                    <div class="admin-card">
                        <h3>Manage Categories</h3>
                        <div id="adminCategoryList"></div>
                        <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:16px;">
                            <input type="text" id="newCategoryInput" placeholder="New category name" style="flex:1;padding:8px 12px;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--font);" />
                            <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" id="addCategoryBtn">Add</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Settings -->
                <div class="admin-section" id="admin-settings">
                    <div class="admin-card">
                        <h3>⚙️ Settings</h3>
                        <div class="toggle-wrap">
                            <span>Dark Mode</span>
                            <div class="toggle" id="adminDarkToggle" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="Toggle dark mode">
                                <div class="knob"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div style="margin-top:16px;padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);">
                            <p class="text-sm text-secondary">Data is stored locally in your browser. Export or import JSON data to migrate.</p>
                            <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
                                <button class="btn btn-sm" id="exportDataBtn">📤 Export Data</button>
                                <button class="btn btn-sm" id="importDataBtn">📥 Import Data</button>
                                <input type="file" id="importFileInput" accept=".json" style="display:none;" />
                                <button class="btn btn-sm" style="color:#FF3B30;" id="resetDataBtn">🗑 Reset All Data</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <!-- SEARCH OVERLAY -->
    <div class="search-overlay" id="searchOverlay" role="dialog" aria-label="Search">
        <div class="search-modal">
            <input type="text" id="searchInput" placeholder="Search books, chapters, categories..." autofocus />
            <div class="results" id="searchResults"></div>
            <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" style="margin-top:12px;width:100%;" id="closeSearch">Close</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- READING MODE -->
    <div class="reader-view" id="readerView" role="dialog" aria-label="Reading mode">
        <div class="reader-toolbar">
            <div class="left">
                <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-icon" id="readerClose" aria-label="Close reader">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
                        <path d="M15 5L5 15M5 5L15 15" />
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <span class="title" id="readerBookTitle">Book Title</span>
            </div>
            <div class="right">
                <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-icon" id="readerToc" aria-label="Table of contents">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
                        <rect x="2" y="3" width="16" height="14" rx="1.5" />
                        <path d="M6 7L14 7M6 10L12 10M6 13L10 13" />
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-icon" id="readerSettingsToggle" aria-label="Reading settings">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
                        <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="2.5" />
                        <path d="M10 2V4M10 16V18M18 10H16M4 10H2M15.07 4.93L13.66 6.34M6.34 13.66L4.93 15.07M15.07 15.07L13.66 13.66M6.34 6.34L4.93 4.93" />
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <div class="reader-settings" id="readerSettings">
                    <div class="setting-group">
                        <label for="readerFontSize">Font Size</label>
                        <input type="range" id="readerFontSize" min="14" max="28" value="18" step="1" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="setting-group">
                        <label for="readerFontFamily">Font</label>
                        <select id="readerFontFamily">
                            <option value="Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif">Serif (Georgia)</option>
                            <option value="-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', sans-serif">Sans-Serif</option>
                            <option value="'Courier New', monospace">Monospace</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="setting-group">
                        <label>Theme</label>
                        <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;">
                            <button class="btn btn-sm reader-theme-btn active" data-theme="light">☀️</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-sm reader-theme-btn" data-theme="dark">🌙</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-sm reader-theme-btn" data-theme="sepia">📜</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reader-content" id="readerContent"></div>

        <div class="reader-footer">
            <div class="nav-buttons">
                <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" id="readerPrev">← Prev</button>
                <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" id="readerNext">Next →</button>
            </div>
            <span class="progress-text" id="readerProgress">0%</span>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:4px;">
                <button class="btn btn-ghost btn-icon" id="readerBookmark" aria-label="Bookmark">
                    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
                        <path d="M4 2H14V16L9 12L4 16V2Z" />
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ============================================================
    JAVASCRIPT (with file upload/download via IndexedDB)
    ============================================================ -->
    <script>
        /**
         * ============================================================
         * BookSphere — Complete Application
         * ============================================================
         * Features:
         *   - Apple-inspired UI with dark mode
         *   - Book management (CRUD) with chapters
         *   - File upload/download (PDF, EPUB, TXT) via IndexedDB
         *   - Reading mode with text & PDF support
         *   - Search, categories, profile, bookmarks, favorites
         *   - Data persistence via localStorage + IndexedDB
         * ============================================================
         */

        // ----- INDEXEDDB FILE STORE ---------------------------------------

        const DB_NAME = 'BookSphereFiles';
        const STORE_NAME = 'files';
        let db = null;

        function openDB() {
            return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
                const request = indexedDB.open(DB_NAME, 1);
                request.onupgradeneeded = (event) => {
                    const db = event.target.result;
                    if (!db.objectStoreNames.contains(STORE_NAME)) {
                        db.createObjectStore(STORE_NAME, { keyPath: 'id' });
                    }
                };
                request.onsuccess = (event) => {
                    db = event.target.result;
                    resolve(db);
                };
                request.onerror = (event) => {
                    reject(event.target.error);
                };
            });
        }

        async function storeFile(id, file) {
            await ensureDB();
            return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
                const tx = db.transaction(STORE_NAME, 'readwrite');
                const store = tx.objectStore(STORE_NAME);
                const record = {
                    id: id,
                    name: file.name,
                    type: file.type || 'application/octet-stream',
                    size: file.size,
                    data: file,
                    lastModified: file.lastModified
                };
                const request = store.put(record);
                request.onsuccess = () => resolve(record);
                request.onerror = () => reject(request.error);
            });
        }

        async function getFile(id) {
            await ensureDB();
            return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
                const tx = db.transaction(STORE_NAME, 'readonly');
                const store = tx.objectStore(STORE_NAME);
                const request = store.get(id);
                request.onsuccess = () => resolve(request.result || null);
                request.onerror = () => reject(request.error);
            });
        }

        async function deleteFile(id) {
            await ensureDB();
            return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
                const tx = db.transaction(STORE_NAME, 'readwrite');
                const store = tx.objectStore(STORE_NAME);
                const request = store.delete(id);
                request.onsuccess = () => resolve();
                request.onerror = () => reject(request.error);
            });
        }

        async function ensureDB() {
            if (!db) {
                await openDB();
            }
            if (!db) {
                throw new Error('IndexedDB not available');
            }
            return db;
        }

        // Convert File to base64 for display
        function fileToBase64(file) {
            return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
                const reader = new FileReader();
                reader.onload = () => resolve(reader.result);
                reader.onerror = () => reject(reader.error);
                reader.readAsDataURL(file);
            });
        }

        // ----- DATA LAYER --------------------------------------------------

        const DEFAULT_CATEGORIES = [
            'History', 'Science', 'Islam', 'Technology',
            'Politics', 'Military', 'Nature', 'AI',
            'Health', 'Business'
        ];

        const SAMPLE_BOOKS = [{
            id: 'book-1',
            title: 'The Art of Islamic Pattern',
            subtitle: 'A Visual Journey Through Geometry and Design',
            author: 'Sarah Al-Hassan',
            category: 'Islam',
            description: 'Explore the rich tradition of Islamic geometric patterns, from the mosques of Cordoba to the palaces of Isfahan.',
            coverEmoji: '🕌',
            chapters: [
                { id: 'ch1', title: 'Introduction to Islamic Geometry',
                    content: '<p>Islamic geometric patterns represent one of the most sophisticated artistic traditions in human history.</p><p>The patterns are built on the principle of repetition and symmetry, reflecting the Islamic concept of tawhid — the oneness of God.</p><blockquote>"Geometry is the language of the universe."</blockquote>' },
                { id: 'ch2', title: 'The Four-Fold Pattern',
                    content: '<p>The four-fold pattern, based on the square and its diagonal, is one of the most fundamental motifs.</p><p>Artists would begin with a square grid, then add diagonal lines to create a complex interlocking design.</p>' }
            ],
            progress: 45,
            published: '2023-05-15',
            fileId: null,
            fileName: null,
            fileType: null,
            fileSize: null
        }, {
            id: 'book-2',
            title: 'Digital Minimalism',
            subtitle: 'Finding Focus in a Noisy World',
            author: 'Cal Newport',
            category: 'Technology',
            description: 'A philosophical and practical guide to reclaiming your attention in the age of digital distraction.',
            coverEmoji: '📱',
            chapters: [
                { id: 'ch1', title: 'The Problem of Digital Noise',
                    content: '<p>We live in an era of unprecedented connectivity. Our devices buzz with notifications.</p><p>This constant interruption fragments our attention and erodes our capacity for deep work.</p>' },
                { id: 'ch2', title: 'The Digital Minimalism Philosophy',
                    content: '<p>Digital minimalism is a philosophy of intentionality. It asks: "What tools are truly valuable to me?"</p>' }
            ],
            progress: 72,
            published: '2024-01-10',
            fileId: null,
            fileName: null,
            fileType: null,
            fileSize: null
        }, {
            id: 'book-3',
            title: 'The Structure of Scientific Revolutions',
            subtitle: 'How Paradigms Shape Discovery',
            author: 'Thomas S. Kuhn',
            category: 'Science',
            description: 'A landmark work in the philosophy of science, arguing that scientific progress occurs through paradigm shifts.',
            coverEmoji: '🔬',
            chapters: [
                { id: 'ch1', title: 'The Role of Paradigms',
                    content: '<p>Paradigms are the shared frameworks of assumptions, methods, and values that define a scientific community.</p>' },
                { id: 'ch2', title: 'Anomaly and Crisis',
                    content: '<p>Anomalies are observations that cannot be explained within the current paradigm.</p>' }
            ],
            progress: 23,
            published: '2022-08-20',
            fileId: null,
            fileName: null,
            fileType: null,
            fileSize: null
        }, {
            id: 'book-4',
            title: 'Political Order and Political Decay',
            subtitle: 'From the Industrial Revolution to the Globalization of Democracy',
            author: 'Francis Fukuyama',
            category: 'Politics',
            description: 'A sweeping history of political development from the French Revolution to the present day.',
            coverEmoji: '🏛️',
            chapters: [
                { id: 'ch1', title: 'The Origins of Political Order',
                    content: '<p>Political order is built on three pillars: a strong state, the rule of law, and accountable government.</p>' },
                { id: 'ch2', title: 'The Challenge of State-Building',
